<li>(1979) <i>Problems</i></li>
<li>(1979) <i><a href="/wiki/Too_Far_To_Go" title="Too Far To Go" class="mw-redirect">Too Far To Go</a></i> (the Maples stories)</li>
<li>(1987) <i><a href="/wiki/Trust_Me_(book)" title="Trust Me (book)">Trust Me</a></i></li>
<li>(1994) <i>The Afterlife</i></li>
<li>(2000) <i>The Best American Short Stories of the Century</i> (editor)</li>
<li>(2001) <i>Licks of Love</i></li>
<li>(2003) <i>The Early Stories: 1953–1975</i></li>
<li>(2009) <i><a href="/wiki/My_Father%27s_Tears_and_Other_Stories" title="My Father's Tears and Other Stories">My Father's Tears and Other Stories</a></i></li>
</ul>
<p><b>Poetry</b></p>
<ul>
