<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/books/remembering-upd/" class="external text" title="http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/books/remembering-upd/" rel="nofollow">Remembering Updike, <i>New Yorker</i></a></li>
