<li><a href="http://www.newyorker.com/talk/2009/02/09/090209ta_talk_gopnik" class="external text" title="http://www.newyorker.com/talk/2009/02/09/090209ta_talk_gopnik" rel="nofollow">Postcript, Adam Gopnik, <i>New Yorker</i>, 9 February 2009</a></li>
