<li><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2009/jan/27/john-updike-obituary" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2009/jan/27/john-updike-obituary" rel="nofollow">John Updike 1932-2009, Eric Homberger, <i>The Guardian</i>, Tuesday 27 January 2009</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/22391" class="external text" title="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/22391" rel="nofollow">On John Updike, Ian McEwan, <i>New York Review of Books</i>, 12 March 2009</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.oxonianreview.org/wp/john-updike-a-self-forever/" class="external text" title="http://www.oxonianreview.org/wp/john-updike-a-self-forever/" rel="nofollow">John Updike: A Self Forever, Jonathan Gharraie, The Oxonian Review, February 9, 2009</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.latimes.com/news/obituaries/la-me-john-updike28-2009jan28,0,3942596.story" class="external text" title="http://www.latimes.com/news/obituaries/la-me-john-updike28-2009jan28,0,3942596.story" rel="nofollow">John Updike dies at 76, Mary Rourke, <i>Los Angeles Time</i>, 28 January 2009</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Pictures" id="Pictures"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=John_Updike&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Pictures">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Pictures</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://todayspictures.slate.com/20090128/" class="external text" title="http://todayspictures.slate.com/20090128/" rel="nofollow">John Updike, RIP</a>&#160;: photographs by <a href="/wiki/Magnum_Photos" title="Magnum Photos">Magnum Photos</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/gallery/2009/jan/27/john-updike?picture=342403954" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/gallery/2009/jan/27/john-updike?picture=342403954" rel="nofollow">A Life in Pictures (15 pictures)</a>, <i>The Guardian</i>, January 2009.</li>
<li><a href="http://newyorksocialdiary.com/node/193849" class="external text" title="http://newyorksocialdiary.com/node/193849" rel="nofollow"><i>New York Social Diary</i>: Jill Krementz Photo Journal - John Updike</a></li>
